<li id="cite_note-33"><b><a href="#cite_ref-33" title="">^</a></b> Wilson 2005</li>
<li id="cite_note-34"><b><a href="#cite_ref-34" title="">^</a></b> Oskar Skarsaune, <i>In the Shadow of the Temple: Jewish Influences on Early Christianity,</i> 319-337.</li>
<li id="cite_note-35"><b><a href="#cite_ref-35" title="">^</a></b> Raymond E Brown, <i>Christ in the Gospels of the Ordinary Sundays,</i> 83-92.</li>
</ol>
</div>
